LONDON
Dong Kingman, the award winning Chinese-American artist, travels the world sketching and painting
the beautiful, the monumental and the picturesque. His watercolors grace more than forty
permanent museum and private collections in the USA and abroad.
This view of the Thames embankment and Big Ben captures some of the charm of London. Ever
student of history should see the Houses of Parliament, Buckingham Palace, Westminster Abbev and
the Tower of London. While it is one of the world's great centers of commerce, it is also a city of
beauty with extensive parks and gardens. The luxurious Inter-Continental London is situated adjacent
to gracious Hyde Park and the Portman Inter-Continental Hotel is conveniently located at One,
Portman Square. Pan Am serves London every day on its Round-The-World flights and one can reach
